tiles.name: DTAQL
tiles.query: select sum(doubleProperties.revenue) as "Risk Revenue" FROM usersession where useraction.name = "Finish" and (useraction.apdexCategory ="TOLERATING" or useraction.apdexCategory ="FRUSTRATED" or useraction.apdexCategory ="UNKNOWN")

tiles.name: DTAQL
tiles.query: select DISTINCT DATETIME(starttime, "HH:mm", "10m") as "Time", sum(doubleProperties.revenue) as "Risk Revenue" FROM usersession where useraction.name = "Finish" and (useraction.apdexCategory ="TOLERATING" or useraction.apdexCategory ="FRUSTRATED" or useraction.apdexCategory ="UNKNOWN")
